{"tid":2136060,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭錦滿：點解直斥張秀賢團伙係政棍？","createTime":"2020-08-01T21:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T09:13:30.000Z","uid":123264,"like":7,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8f16e0a59acd03d7f251ca36381a96bdced633e8","tid":2136060,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T21:46:56.000Z","msg":"張秀賢 2017 年成立議政組織「立言香港 LAB IN HK」，組織簡介寫明「不以參加選舉或走入建制為目標」，但係召集人張秀賢、委員巫堃泰、委員張崑陽分別加入「不同派系」參與選舉，咁樣唔係政治投機係咩呢？<br />\n<br />\n當然，你可以話「組織」同「個人」唔一樣，咁民建聯、工聯會係咪共產黨呀？建制政棍喺唔同建制政黨之間走嚟走去，係咪都執行緊共產黨嘅任務？<br />\n<br />\n睇真啲 #七二一 之前張秀賢嘅訪問啦，因為「社運低迷」，人哋一早「棄政從商」啦。咁樣唔係投機政棍係咩呢？<br />\n因為 7.21 而成為投機政棍嘅都唔止佢一個，今日就招呼住你先。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/116133394_3246127535449218_169553304813948379_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=mFt0eWU_ifsAX9rFzkp&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=66f178e55fd5518dfa123d2e3b551998&amp;oe=5F4C3528\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F116133394_3246127535449218_169553304813948379_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3DmFt0eWU_ifsAX9rFzkp%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D66f178e55fd5518dfa123d2e3b551998%26oe%3D5F4C3528&h=a32a7c84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仆街熱狗又搞分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f55bf7b5af3e2118179f6938d65454c5d8c51e2","tid":2136060,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T21:52:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c9f7281a9a6dc2890a66d44d88bc28097a627b7","tid":2136060,"uid":325346,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T21:59:44.000Z","msg":"佢自己咪又係政棍<br />\n咁叻咪撚入閘選舉<br />\n搞到無左三十萬選舉開支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23676c520d740e18c4573a1bf049b300eb23f205","tid":2136060,"uid":123264,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote